WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.500
Anna is living with her family in one 
 of the many miners' settlements in the Ruhr area.

00:04.500 --> 00:08.167
There are run-down little houses 
 where large families live.

00:08.167 --> 00:13.500
Next to them are small gardens where the workers'
 families grow vegetables and keep livestock.

00:13.500 --> 00:18.150
As more and more people from other parts of the country
 come to the Ruhr area in the hope of finding work,

00:18.200 --> 00:20.833
beds are sometimes sublet to so-called bed lodgers.
